snippet.title: Dinos Reborn - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1522360/Dinos_Reborn/
Dinos Reborn is an open-world FPP survival game in a sci-fi setting with a mind-blowing storyline and intriguing mechanics, where you can turn from being a hunter to prey in a matter of seconds. Run, sneak, craft and shoot to survive to uncover a great mystery.

Join a growing community of Hunters on Discord Server:
https://discord.gg/2mKkmvrK4u

Check our Social Media to stay tuned with game development:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DinosReborn
Twitter https://twitter.com/Dinos_Reborn

Publisher Social Media:
https://www.facebook.com/VisionEdgeEntertainment
https://twitter.com/VisionEdgeEnt


#DinosReborn #game #trailer #survival #dinosaurs #openworld
